Arlete Guilhermina "Guillermina" Vincente Bombe (a mụrụ n'afọ 1983) bụ onye Mozambican na-eme ihe nkiri si Maputo, Mozambique.
N'afọ 2017, e gosipụtara ya na ihe ngosi Iacopo Patierno nke akpọrọ, Wiwanana, n'akụkụ Safina Ansumane Ali, Agostino Maico Chipula na ndị ọzọ.
E gosipụtakwara ya na ihe nkiri Mickey Fonseca nke afọ 2019 nke nwetara ihe nrite, Redemption ("Resgate" na Portuguese)
Ihe nkiri ahụ gosipụtakwara Gil Alexandre, Laquino Fonseca, Tomas Bie, Rachide Abul, Candido Quembo na ndị ọzọ.
A họpụtara ya na AMAA 2019 Award For Best Actress in a Supporting Role category na 15th Africa Movie Academy Awards (AMAA), maka ọrụ ya na ihe nkiri, Redemption
